---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="Privacy notes for ryanbaird.com."
  structuredData={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    name: "Privacy",
    url: "https://ryanbaird.com/privacy/",
  }}
>
  <section class="section prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p>
      This site is a personal portfolio and blog. It is designed to collect as little
      information as possible while still working reliably.
    </p>

    <h2>Server Logs</h2>
    <p>
      The site runs on Cloudflare Workers. Cloudflare may process standard request
      information such as IP address, user agent, requested URL, timestamp, and basic
      security signals to deliver the site and protect the service.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      There is no first-party analytics script installed right now. If analytics are added,
      the preference is cookieless, privacy-respecting measurement.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      This site does not intentionally set tracking cookies. Some platform-level behavior may
      change if interactive features are added later.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you contact me directly, I will use the information you provide to respond to that
      message. I do not sell personal information.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
